ENA.AX.summary: Ensurance Limited engages in the underwriting and sale of insurance products in Australia and the United Kingdom. The company provides contractors-all risk, contractors-plant and equipment, home build, combined liability, contractors assist, engineering inspection and insurance, construction, cyber, and terrorism and sabotage insurance products. It also offers underwriting services, including licensed builder annual construction, plant, and liability insurance; and licensed builder project specific construction insurance, trades liability, owner builder, and latent defect products. In addition, the company trades insurance products through online platform. Ensurance Limited is based in Bondi Junction, Australia.

SDF.AX.summary: Steadfast Group Limited provides general insurance brokerage services Australasia, Asia, and Europe. It also provides insurance underwriting services and related services. The company operates a network of 458 general insurance brokers and 25 underwriting agencies. Steadfast Group Limited was founded in 1996 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
